//! Acceptance test for AC3 (MUST) — generated by `autobuilder scaffold`.
//!
//! Project: mqo-eval (cli)
//! AC description: --agent '<cmd>' substitutes the binder subprocess; stub binder (echo fixed JSON) works in CI without real mqo-agent binary
//! Test predicate: cargo test -- ac3_stub_binder
//!
//! Ownership split: this //! header block (AC metadata) is
//! read-only — to change an AC, file
//! agent/intent_card_amendment_request.json and re-scaffold. The
//! `fn acceptance_ac3` body BELOW is owned by the edit-agent: replace
